ghly 15 seconds. Though I am confident that I would have been able to get the initial round of combat + bs before that.  Chances are however high that if it really did enough dmg the wiz would simply yonder and wait for a better oportunity to kill.<br><br>No golem wands were used in this engagement because the target had yondered and recast epic when I had tried that shortly before.<br><br>Some time was wasted trying to do dmg with non lure spells that could have been far better spent on lures.<br><br>Voltaic was attempting to spell spam me to lag me to gain an advantage that way but it wasn't having a signifigant effect.<br><br>Info...<br><br>Spells cast by voltaic 4 interuped by me 0.  Lead time per spell after the first cast from a distance was around 2 seconds.<br><br>Spell dmg...<br>Sunstrike-Resisted, lol fluke there<br>Lure of ice- 561 dmg<br>Soloist ice spear- 357<br>Lure of ice- 534<br><br>Total 1482<br>dps 67<br><br>Total dmg by me- &lt;800 dps 36(guessing)<br><br>Why so low? Simple he's not casting the entire time he's moving too.  When he's not casting I'm not able to hit him cause he's on the move. In addition there is a short space between him starting to cast and me starting hitting him.  So I am only able to for example hit him for 2.5-3 seconds out of a 4.5 sec cast or 2-2.5 out of a 4 second. My total dps while hitting him in this case was probably around 70.<br><br><br><br>In conclusion he in this log is basicly hurting me twice as fast as I'm hurting him and with epic skin and good armor he probably has as much if not more dmg absorption than I do.  Removing a wizards epic skin outdoors becomes basicly impossible as its very very simple to yonder off and reapply it wasting no manna.  Not true of skins that require manna as it will burn through the casters manna supply (and plat).<br><br>I estimate I would be able to do about 1k dmg to him before he killed me if we had continued on, a substantial portion of it would have been absorbed.<br><br>Indoors it would have been possible to to golem wand him knowing he wouldn't be able to yonder and reapply and there would have been less lead time between spells.  60 wizards are however by no means underpowered outdoors.  <br><br>Indoors ya still have gate and lvl 4 spells basicly never get interupted (except by death) without bash.<br><br><br>-----------LOG BEGINS-----------<br><br>Apr 12 21:16:25 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:25 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:25 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:25 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:25 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:26 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:26 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:26 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:26 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:26 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:26 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:27 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:27 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:27 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:27 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:43 2002] Latnim says out of character, 'run'<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:48 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:49 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:49 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:49 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:49 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:49 2002] You say out of character, 'lol '<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:49 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>[Fri Apr 12 21:16:49 2002] You resist the LowerElement spell!<br>